title: The Grave Digger (v1.07) -[GIBZ]
description:
This is: The Grave Digger (v1.07)

Kinda creepy, with a little stealth going on. One reviewer'd said this on the game: "Interesting, from the name I thought this was a bizarre grave digging simulator. But than I see it's more like that weird little game where you played a mad scientist and had to dig graves to make an undead wife for yourself".
UUUUuuuuuuuuuuhhhh, I'll take it!!
--------------------------------------

Description:
Take control of shovel-master Fagus the grave robber extraordinaire in this third person stealth action-adventure. It's a curious blend of whimsical English comedy and grim Dickensian horror made by a two-man team dedicated to fun, addictive gameplay.
